trans-unit.source: A "path expression" is a name or other primary, possibly qualified by various forms of dot, and/or followed by various kinds of brackets. It can be used for value or assigned to, or else further qualified, indexed, or called. It is called a "path" because it looks like a linear path through a data structure. Examples: x.y, x?.y, x*.y, x.@y; x[], x[y], x[y,z]; x(), x(y), x(y,z); x{s}; a.b[n].c(x).d{s} (Compare to a C lvalue, or LeftHandSide in the JLS section 15.26.) General expressions are built up from path expressions, using operators like '+' and '='.
trans-unit.target: 一个 "路径表达式 "是一个名称或其他主词,可能用各种形式的点来限定,和/或在后面加上各种括号。它可以用来取值或赋值,或者进一步限定、索引或调用。它被称为 "路径",因为它看起来像一条穿过数据结构的线性路径。例子:x.y,x?.y,x*.y,x.@y;x[],x[y],x[y,z];x(),x(y),x(y,z);x{s};a.b[n].c(x).d{s}(比较C lvalue,或JLS第15.26节中的LeftHandSide。)一般表达式是由路径表达式建立起来的,使用'+'和'='等运算符。

trans-unit.source: A BSF Engine for the Groovy scripting language.
A Caching implementation of the GroovyEngine

A ClassLoader which can load Groovy classes. The loaded classes are cached, classes from other classloaders should not be cached. To be able to load a script that was asked for earlier but was created later it is essential not to keep anything like a "class not found" information for that class name. This includes possible parent loaders. Classes that are not cached are always reloaded.
trans-unit.target: 一个可以加载Groovy类的ClassLoader。加载的类会被缓存,来自其他类加载器的类不应该被缓存。为了能够加载一个之前被要求但后来被创建的脚本,不要为该类名保留任何类似 "类未找到 "的信息是非常必要的。这包括可能的父类加载器。没有被缓存的类总是会被重新加载。

trans-unit.source: A ClassNode should be created using the methods in ClassHelper. This ClassNode may be used to represent a class declaration or any other type. This class uses a proxy mechanism allowing to create a class for a plain name at AST creation time. In another phase of the compiler the real ClassNode for the plain name may be found. To avoid the need of exchanging this ClassNode with an instance of the correct ClassNode the correct ClassNode is set as redirect. Most method calls are then redirected to that ClassNode.
trans-unit.target: 应该使用ClassHelper中的方法创建一个ClassNode。这个ClassNode可以用来代表一个类声明或任何其他类型。这个类使用一个代理机制,允许在AST创建时为一个纯名创建一个类。在编译器的另一个阶段,可以找到真正的明文名称的ClassNode。为了避免与正确的ClassNode实例交换这个ClassNode,正确的ClassNode被设置为重定向。然后,大多数方法调用都会被重定向到该ClassNode。
